    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade BMW E46 M3, showcasing the pinnacle of atmospheric S54 engineering. This chassis remains structurally pristine, with the critical rear subframe reinforcement already professionally executed. The high-revving 3.2L inline-six features a fully overhauled double-VANOS system and updated rod bearings, ensuring peak volumetric efficiency and mechanical longevity through the 8,000 RPM sweep. Power is delivered via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a factory limited-slip differential. This example retains its original factory paint depth and boasts a flawless interior, representing a turn-key acquisition for the discerning collector and performance purist.",
