    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare find for a discerning collector or enthusiast: a truly showroom-quality vehicle that has been meticulously preserved since day one. Finished in a deep, lustrous metallic paint that has been protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating, the exterior is absolutely flawless with no chips, dings, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin remains in 'as-new' condition; the premium leather upholstery is supple with zero bolster wear, and the original factory fragrance still lingers. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach. Every service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships, with a comprehensive folder of records included. It drives with the same precision, tightness, and smoothness as the day it was delivered. Garaged in a climate-controlled environment and never driven in inclement weather, this car represents the absolute pinnacle of its model year. If you are looking for a museum-grade example that requires zero excuses, this is the one.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
