    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a bit sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy this absolute gem. It\u2019s in truly pristine condition\u2014honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve pampered this car since day one, keeping it garage-kept and spotless. It drives like a dream and still even has that new-car smell. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been deeply loved and looks totally flawless, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out if you want to come see it in person!",
